author: Joshua Espinoza
title: Are Chance the Rapper and Childish Gambino Working on New Music?
text:
Watch Childish Gambino and Chance The Rapper Trade off Impressive Freestyles During a Concert in Chicago On Monday night, Chance posted an Instagram photo of himself standing next to Childish. He captioned the image: “Hawaii then LA, back to work. #roscoeswetsuit.” For those of you who don’t know “Roscoe’s wetsuit” is a reference to Childish’s Because the Internet screenplay , co-starring Chance. It’s unclear if the two are working on something related to the short film or finally completing that long-awaited tape. There's also a chance they were just catching up during the holidays, and aren’t collaborating on anything at all. Nevertheless, this post has definitely got fans' hopes up. You can check out some of the Twitter reactions below. 
a chance childish album is going to melt my brain and I'm so excited @chancetherapper @donaldglover —11th wonder☯™ (@ps_dwyw) January 3, 2017

If this Chance X Childish tape comes out this year I will be in tears.
